casebody.data:
Terron HOOKS, Appellant,
v.
STATE of Missouri, Respondent. WD 81575 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: June 28, 2019 S. Kate Webber, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Mary Moore, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Before Division Three: Thomas H. Newton, P.J., Anthony Rex Gabbert, and Edward R. Ardini, JJ.

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Mr. Terron Hooks appeals a Jackson County Circuit Court judgment overruling a Rule 24.035 motion following an evidentiary hearing. For the reasons stated in the memorandum provided to the parties, we affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
